ort|Koh Samui]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Batik Air]] | [[Chennai International Airport|Chennai]],<ref>https://amp.kompas.com/ekonomi/read/2017/08/27/093200926/garap-wisman-india-batik-air-buka-rute-ke-chennai-</ref><ref>https://kompas.id/baca/utama/2017/08/26/batik-air-buka-rute-medan-kuala-lumpur-chennai/</ref> [[Ngurah Rai International Airport|Denpasar/Bali]],<ref name=\"Batik_Chennai\">{{cite web|url=http://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/273507/batik-air-plans-chennai-service-from-july-2017/|title=Batik Air plans Chennai service from July 2017|publisher=routesonline|accessdate=27 June 2017}}</ref> [[Soekarno-Hatta International Airport|Jakarta-Soekarno-Hatta]],<ref>http://m.harnas.co/2019/10/22/batik-air-buka-rute-cengkareng-kuala-lumpur</ref> [[Kualanamu International Airport|Medan]]<ref name=\"Batik_Chennai\">{{cite web|url=http://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/273507/batik-air-plans-chennai-service-from-july-2017/|title=Batik Air plans Chennai service from July 2017|publisher=routesonline|accessdate=27 June 2017}}</ref><ref>https://amp.kompas.com/ekonomi/read/2017/08/27/093200926/garap-wisman-india-batik-air-buka-rute-ke-chennai-</ref><ref>https://kompas.id/baca/utama/2017/08/26/batik-air-buka-rute-medan-kuala-lumpur-chennai/</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| {{nowrap|[[Biman Bangladesh Airlines]]}} | [[Shahjalal International Airport|Dhaka]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[British Airways]] | [[Heathrow Airport|London\u2013Heathrow]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Cathay Dragon]] | [[Hong Kong International Airport|Hong Kong]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Cebu Pacific]] | [[Ninoy Aquino International Airport|Manila]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[China Airlines]] | [[Taiwan Taoyuan International Airport|Taipei\u2013Taoyuan]]\n<!-- -->\n| {{nowrap|[[China Southern Airlines]]}} | [[Changsha Huanghua International Airport|Changsha]], [[Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport|Guangzhou]], [[Xining Caojiabao International Airport|Xining]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yushunews.com/system/2017/10/31/012455806.shtml |script-titl