pur-route.html</ref> [[Banyuwangi International Airport|Banyuwangi]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.banyuwangikab.go.id/berita-daerah/19-desember-rute-internasional-kuala-lumpur-banyuwangi-resmi-dibuka.html |title=19 Desember, rute Internasional Kuala Lumpur-Banyuwangi resmi dibuka |publisher=Banyuwangikab.go.id |date= |accessdate=2018-12-17}}</ref> [[Ngurah Rai International Airport|Denpasar/Bali]],<ref>https://www.citilink.co.id/rute-dps-kul</ref> [[Soekarno\u2013Hatta International Airport|Jakarta\u2013Soekarno-Hatta]], [[Sultan Syarif Kasim II International Airport|Pekanbaru]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Citilink files Pekanbaru \u2013 Kuala Lumpur schedule from late-Sep 2019 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/286200/citilink-files-pekanbaru-kuala-lumpur-schedule-from-late-sep-2019/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=5 September 2019}}</ref> [[Juanda International Airport|Surabaya]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Emirates (airline)|Emirates]] | [[Dubai International Airport|Dubai\u2013International]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Ethiopian Airlines]] | [[Addis Ababa Bole International Airport|Addis Ababa]], [[Suvarnabhumi Airport|Bangkok\u2013Suvarnabhumi]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Ethiopian Airlines NS20 South East Asia routing changes|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/289106/ethiopian-airlines-ns20-south-east-asia-routing-changes/|website=Routesonline |accessdate=31 January 2020}}</ref> [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Etihad Airways]] | [[Abu Dhabi International Airport|Abu Dhabi]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[EVA Air]] | [[Taiwan Taoyuan International Airport|Taipei\u2013Taoyuan]] \n<!-- -->\n| [[Garuda Indonesia]] | [[Soekarno\u2013Hatta International Airport|Jakarta\u2013Soekarno-Hatta]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Gulf Air]] | [[Bahrain International Airport|Bahrain]] (resumes 3 July 2020)<ref>{{cite web|last=Liu|date=17 December 2019|accessdate=17 December 2019|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlinerout